00:01:58.176 --> 00:02:01.246 A:middle
Kids are beset by a
world on the internet

00:02:01.246 --> 00:02:02.976 A:middle
where there are millions
of strangers

00:02:02.976 --> 00:02:05.606 A:middle
out there they can have
instantaneous contact

00:02:05.606 --> 00:02:08.406 A:middle
with both other kids
and grownups.

00:02:08.866 --> 00:02:11.936 A:middle
