00:03:58.556 --> 00:04:00.016 A:middle
to the App Store
sessions or labs

00:04:00.016 --> 00:04:01.506 A:middle
and learn a little
bit more about these.

00:04:01.876 --> 00:04:04.916 A:middle
If you're targeting your
apps to sell to the parents

00:04:05.226 --> 00:04:08.566 A:middle
of young kids who are going
to use them there's a couple

00:04:08.566 --> 00:04:11.196 A:middle
of things you need to do
to get into that category.

00:04:11.566 --> 00:04:13.786 A:middle
You have to have a
privacy policy on your page

00:04:13.786 --> 00:04:18.055 A:middle
and you've got to link to that
privacy policy on your app page.

00:04:18.386 --> 00:04:21.666 A:middle
You cannot have behavioral
oriented advertising.

00:04:21.946 --> 00:04:23.566 A:middle
You can have contextual
advertising,

00:04:23.566 --> 00:04:27.036 A:middle
but not behavioral oriented
advertising the tracks your kid.

00:04:27.036 --> 00:04:31.606 A:middle
You can do no tracking
across sites or across apps.

00:04:31.606 --> 00:04:34.926 A:middle
The contextual ads must
be appropriate for kids

00:04:35.336 --> 00:04:37.426 A:middle
and you've got to
have a parental gate

00:04:37.426 --> 00:04:40.146 A:middle
on your app before you
get out of the app to go

00:04:40.146 --> 00:04:44.846 A:middle
to In-App Purchases back to the
App Store or to any online site.

00:04:45.296 --> 00:04:48.146 A:middle
So again, little
cul-de-sacs of functionality

00:04:48.146 --> 00:04:50.776 A:middle
to accommodate kids
using our technology.

00:04:51.686 --> 00:04:56.046 A:middle
But there is a lot going on
in the world and a lot going

00:04:56.046 --> 00:05:00.676 A:middle
on in the United States about
what technology companies,


