00:32:39.986 --> 00:32:41.376 A:middle
before you can allow your app

00:32:41.676 --> 00:32:44.086 A:middle
to collect personally
identifying information

00:32:44.276 --> 00:32:44.936 A:middle
from the kid.

00:32:45.376 --> 00:32:48.626 A:middle
Do the same thing worldwide,
it'll be a lot more convenient

00:32:48.626 --> 00:32:51.306 A:middle
and it'll be a lot more
consistent and prepare you

00:32:51.306 --> 00:32:52.936 A:middle
for what's going to
happen in the future.

